units.contents:
[Unit]
Description=Run after install
After=network-online.target
Wants=network-online.target

[Service]
Type=oneshot
ExecStart=/usr/local/bin/post-install-hook
ExecStart=systemctl disable post-install-hook
ExecStart=rm -f /var/usrlocal/bin/post-install-hook
ExecStart=rm -f /etc/systemd/system/post-install-hook.service
ExecStart=/usr/bin/systemctl --no-block reboot
StandardOutput=kmsg+console
StandardError=kmsg+console

[Install]
RequiredBy=default.target
units.name: post-install-hook.service
